# ===== StreamingIP 流媒体 IP 段规则配方 =====
# 聚合 metacubex geoip/netflix (主源)
# 注: 其他流媒体 (Disney+/Spotify 等) 多走 CDN,缺独立 geoip 段

+ list https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MetaCubeX/meta-rules-dat/meta/geo/geoip/netflix.list

# 备选聚合 (取消注释可启用):
# + list https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MetaCubeX/meta-rules-dat/meta/geo/geoip/google.list
# + list https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MetaCubeX/meta-rules-dat/meta/geo/geoip/twitter.list